                        "__cdata": "a:3:{i:1587488620579;s:427:\"<p>An outgoing interstate case may be necessary when you are working a case and the payor lives, works, or has assets in a state other than Iowa.</p>\n<p>If no interstate referral exists with another state, review the following screens before proceeding to make a referral:</p>\n\n[ninja_tables id=\"1629\"]\n\n<p>If referral is necessary, see Outgoing Enforcement for instructions on completing the referral.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\";i:1587488620900;s:493:\"<p>An outgoing interstate case may be necessary when you are working a case and the payor lives, works, or has assets in a state other than Iowa.</p>\n<p>If a current referral exists with another state, check the following screens:</p>\n\n[ninja_tables id=\"1636\"]\n\n<p>After you contact the other state, continue to monitor the case for payments.</p>\n<p><b>Note:</b> In order to improve our customer service, we recommend that you keep the customer advised of any progress on the case.</p>\n\";i:1587494065457;s:0:\"\";}"
